# CODEOWNERS - Require security team approval for sensitive files
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Workflow files require security team approval
/.github/workflows/ @your-org/security-team
/ci/ @your-org/security-team

# Infrastructure changes require platform team approval
/infra/ @your-org/platform-team @your-org/security-team

# Security configurations require security team approval
/security/ @your-org/security-team

# Dockerfile changes require security review
**/Dockerfile @your-org/security-team

# Default owners for everything else
* @your-org/platform-team
